<subSubSection id="C3647DACFFD0AE64C1D5FFB9FBEFA9F5" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BC12E27FFD0AE64C1D5FFB9FBEFA9F5" blockId="35.[151,1436,158,653]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
REMARKS: There are two original spellings of this genus-group name in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFEF53D6FFD0AE64C2AEFFB9FB37AAB2" author="Rondani, C." box="[1004,1194,432,458]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" refId="ref145931" refString="Rondani, C. (1863) Diptera exotica revisa et annotata novis nonnullis descriptis. Eredi Soliani, Modena. 99 pp., 1 pl. [31 December +] [The title page has &quot; nonnullis &quot; but page 1 has &quot; nonullis &quot;. This is the separate that came out before the journal version with a different title, here as Rondani (1864 a).]" type="book" year="1863">Rondani (1863)</bibRefCitation>
: 
<taxonomicName id="4C7E55A4FFD0AE64C5F7FFB9FAB9AAB1" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1863" box="[1205,1316,432,457]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Orobanchaceae" genus="Bellardia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B90AF235FFD0AE64C5F7FFB9FAB9AAB1" box="[1205,1316,432,457]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Bellardia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(page 81) and 
<taxonomicName id="4C7E55A4FFD0AE64C06BFFDEFE04AA88" box="[297,409,471,496]" class="Insecta" family="Tachinidae" genus="Ballardia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B90AF235FFD0AE64C06BFFDEFE04AA88" box="[297,409,471,496]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Ballardia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(page 81). Acting as 
<emphasis id="B90AF235FFD0AE64C3D4FFDEFCA5AA89" bold="true" box="[662,824,471,497]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">First Reviser</emphasis>
, we select 
<taxonomicName id="4C7E55A4FFD0AE64C2F9FFDEFBB7AA88" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1863" box="[955,1066,471,496]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Orobanchaceae" genus="Bellardia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B90AF235FFD0AE64C2F9FFDEFBB7AA88" box="[955,1066,471,496]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Bellardia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as the correct original spelling, which relegates 
<taxonomicName id="4C7E55A4FFD0AE64C08EFFF7FDA1A96F" box="[460,572,510,535]" class="Insecta" family="Tachinidae" genus="Ballardia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B90AF235FFD0AE64C08EFFF7FDA1A96F" box="[460,572,510,535]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Ballardia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<emphasis id="B90AF235FFD0AE64C31AFFF7FDFAA96F" box="[600,615,510,535]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">q</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B90AF235FFD0AE64C32CFFF7FDE6A96F" box="[622,635,510,535]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">v</emphasis>
.) to unavailable name status. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFEF53D6FFD0AE64C553FFF7FAC1A960" author="Robineau-Desvoidy, J. - B." box="[1041,1372,510,536]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" refId="ref142413" refString="Robineau-Desvoidy, J. - B. (1863) Histoire naturelle des dipteres des environs de Paris. Oeuvre posthume du Dr Robineau- Desvoidy publiee par les soins de sa famille, sous la direction de M. H. Monceaux. [Two volumes published simultaneously]. xvi + 1143 pp.; and 920 pp. [11 January] [See Evenhuis et al. (2010 b) for details on dating.]" type="book" year="1863">Robineau-Desvoidy (1863)</bibRefCitation>
was published on 11 January (
<bibRefCitation id="EFEF53D6FFD0AE64C36AFC2CFCA7A947" author="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; O'Hara, J. E. &amp; Pape, T. &amp; Pont, A. C." box="[552,826,549,575]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" refId="ref130296" refString="Evenhuis, N. L., O'Hara, J. E., Pape, T. &amp; Pont, A. C. (2010 b) Nomenclatural studies toward a world catalog of Diptera genusgroup names. Part I. Andre-Jean-Baptiste Robineau-Desvoidy. Zootaxa, 2373, 265 pp. [26 February]" type="book" year="2010">
Evenhuis 
<emphasis id="B90AF235FFD0AE64C3E2FC2CFD4EA946" box="[672,723,549,574]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">et al</emphasis>
., 2010b
</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="EFEF53D6FFD0AE64C20CFC2CFB94A947" author="Rondani, C." box="[846,1033,549,575]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" refId="ref145931" refString="Rondani, C. (1863) Diptera exotica revisa et annotata novis nonnullis descriptis. Eredi Soliani, Modena. 99 pp., 1 pl. [31 December +] [The title page has &quot; nonnullis &quot; but page 1 has &quot; nonullis &quot;. This is the separate that came out before the journal version with a different title, here as Rondani (1864 a).]" type="book" year="1863">Rondani (1863)</bibRefCitation>
has not been accurately dated but (based on receipts of it by Italian scientific societies in early 1864) is presumed to have been published late in the year 1863, and surely after 
<bibRefCitation id="EFEF53D6FFD0AE64C269FC7AFBF2A9F5" author="Robineau-Desvoidy, J. - B." box="[811,1135,627,653]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" refId="ref142413" refString="Robineau-Desvoidy, J. - B. (1863) Histoire naturelle des dipteres des environs de Paris. Oeuvre posthume du Dr Robineau- Desvoidy publiee par les soins de sa famille, sous la direction de M. H. Monceaux. [Two volumes published simultaneously]. xvi + 1143 pp.; and 920 pp. [11 January] [See Evenhuis et al. (2010 b) for details on dating.]" type="book" year="1863">Robineau-Desvoidy (1863)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
